                        tbody
                          tr
                            th.dark-blue-bg(scope='row', width='10%') Claims Process
                            td(width='44%')
                              | Slow and time-consuming manual processing of all steps:
                              ul
                                li Input of receipts and expense data - slow and prone to error. 
                                li Creating expense reports,  - Submitting and discussing reports,
                                li Gaining approvals, and manual processing.
                            td(width='2%')
                              | &rarr;
                            td(width='44%')
                              | Quick to execute steps, within a streamlined process:
                              ul
                                li
                                  | Scan expenses via mobile APP (99% fapiao recognition), to save time and increase expense input accuracy.
                                li
                                  | Mobile App collects expenses for report submittals to be routed automatically for easy approval and processing.
                          tr
                            th.dark-blue-bg(scope='row') Receipt Validation
                            td
                              ul
                                li Verifying genuine receipts is time consuming,
                                li Redo&rsquo;s due to improper receipts is a time-loss. 
                                li Gaining approvals, and manual processing.
                            td
                              | &rarr;
                            td
                              ul
                                li
                                  | Scanned expenses via mobile APP already auto-validated with the tax bureau system at time of submission.
                                li Can automatically identify previously submitted fapiaos. 
                          tr
                            th.dark-blue-bg(scope='row') Internal Control
                            td
                              ul
                                li
                                  | Depends on manual verifications of many steps: receipt validity; expense allocation to category; matching the receipt to the claim;
                                li
                                  | Often hindered by knowledge gaps between departments about expenses, and across the languages of receipt, submitters and approvers.
                            td
                              | &rarr;
                            td
                              ul
                                li Expenses allocated to match your COA categories (flexible to configure).
                                li
                                  | Bilingual CHN-ENG APP allows expense, submission and approval steps be performed across languages, case by case.
                          tr
                            th.dark-blue-bg(scope='row') Reports 
                            td
                              ul
                                li Historical cost analyses are challenging to manually compile 
                                li Analysis of spend trends and details is difficult 
                                li - Graphical representations if any are manually &ldquo;built&rdquo;. 
                            td
                              | &rarr;
                            td
                              ul
                                li Historical expense reports available within the APP
                                li Cross-period reporting and drill down detail 
                                li Graphical analysis to provide quicker trend insights
                          tr
                            th.dark-blue-bg(scope='row') Data Capture
                            td
                              ul
                                li Expense transactions entered manually into ERP system
                                li Limited amount of data enters system 
                                li Risk of human error is higher 
                            td
                              | &rarr;
                            td
                              ul
                                li Scan fapiaos with phone camera
                                li Data synced with AP and T&amp;E modules in ERP 
                                li Subsequent GL transactions populated from these modules 
                                li Far lower risk of manual entry error 
                          tr
                            th.dark-blue-bg(scope='row') Scalability 
                            td
                              | As you grow to larger operational scales,
                              ul
                                li Processing workloads increases in step with scale. 
                                li
                                  | Managing internal controls compounds in its increased importance and difficulty, without the right digital systems.
                            td
                              | &rarr;
                            td
                              | As you grow to larger operational scales,
                              ul
                                li Workloads decrease, compounding efficiency optimization
                                li Data synced with AP and T&amp;E modules in ERP 
                                li
                                  | Managing internal controls remains inherently improved, while processes are adaptable to more stringent measures.



